{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 00:37:30 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T00:37:30Z", "created_at_ts": 1690591050, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685087116311527424", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 130, \"reply_count\": 53, \"like_count\": 980, \"quote_count\": 10, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "If a Supreme Court justice can’t find the provision that gives Congress the authority to regulate SCOTUS then I have some follow-up questions.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:01 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:01Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597621, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114675296620544", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 311, \"reply_count\": 29, \"like_count\": 910, \"quote_count\": 43, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "Planning on seeing Oppenheimer this weekend? Well, I have an important update on the story the movie didn’t tell.\n\nThe film showed a remote test site in the New Mexico desert. An isolated area 210 miles south of Los Alamos, according to government accounts.\n\nNot quite. 🧵", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:01 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:01Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597621, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114676533981184", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 36, \"reply_count\": 2, \"like_count\": 276, \"quote_count\": 0, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "As many as 500,000 people lived within 150 miles of the test site, with some only 12 miles away. None were warned, and none were evacuated before or after Trinity.\n\nThe fallout reached 46 states, and the blast was felt as far as 200 miles away. Ash fell from the sky for days.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:01 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:01Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597621, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114677813301248", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 28, \"reply_count\": 3, \"like_count\": 271, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "In the Tularosa Basin, those now known as Downwinders were exposed to dangerous levels of radiation, marking them and their descendants w/ tragedy ever since. They developed cancers and other illnesses. Infant mortality spiked.\n\n78 years later, they’ve still not been compensated.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:02 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:02Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597622, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114679012855808", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 29, \"reply_count\": 2, \"like_count\": 254, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "In 1990, the Radiation Exposure Compensation Act was passed, establishing a federal fund for people affected by radiation exposure.\n\nFor reasons I can’t even begin to understand, New Mexico Downwinders were excluded.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:02 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:02Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597622, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114680304664576", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 27, \"reply_count\": 2, \"like_count\": 234, \"quote_count\": 0, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "How is it possible that the communities at the center of the first nuclear test were not covered by a program designed for those harmed by nuclear tests?\n\nWell, I promised an update…", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T15:46:21.799436Z", "created_at": "Sat Jul 29 02:27:02 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-07-29T02:27:02Z", "created_at_ts": 1690597622, "display_name": "Martin Heinrich", "handle": "martinheinrich", "id": "1685114681609125888", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 56, \"reply_count\": 6, \"like_count\": 589, \"quote_count\": 4, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "For a decade now, @BenRayLujan has been leading the charge to expand RECA and finally give what is owed to our Downwinders.\n\nYesterday, his amendment passed the Senate. Now it’s on its way to the House. We are so close to getting this signed into law. \n\nLet's get it done.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "MartinHeinrich"}
